"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when they explicitly call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","isActive":true},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text"